    "description": "World Holdings Co., Ltd. engages in human resources and education, information and telecommunications, real estate, and agricultural park businesses in Japan. The company offers subcontracting; business process outsourcing; temporary staffing services; research and development; manufacturing; development of electromechanical designs; development of information technology system designs; and medical and biotechnology research and development. It is also involved in planning, development, sale of condominiums; renovation of condominiums/detached houses; rental property brokerage and real estate brokerage business; development, manufacturing, sale, and rental of prefabricated houses; real estate fund management; and management and collection of receivables. In addition, the company engages in operation of mobile phone store and call center; and management of agricultural parks. The company was formerly known as WORLD INTEC Co., Ltd. The company was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Fukuoka City, Japan."
